ETINUE FOLLOWERS TABLE</b></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;background-color:rgb(209,200,166);text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;width:40px;height:0px;"><b>D6</b></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;background-color:rgb(209,200,166);text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;width:300px;height:0px;"><b>Brayherds</b></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;background-color:rgb(209,200,166);text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;width:300px;height:0px;"><b>Monstrous Beastherds</b></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;width:40px;height:0px;">1</td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;width:300px;height:0px;">20 <a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/beasts-of-chaos/Ungors">Ungors</a></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;width:300px;height:0px;"><a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/beasts-of-chaos/Razorgors">Razorgor</a></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;background-color:rgb(242,238,225);text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;width:40px;height:0px;">2</td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;background-color:rgb(242,238,225);text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;width:300px;height:0px;">5 <a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/beasts-of-chaos/Centigors">Centigors</a></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;background-color:rgb(242,238,225);text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;width:300px;height:0px;">10 <a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/beasts-of-chaos/Chaos-Warhounds">Chaos Warhounds</a></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;width:40px;height:0px;">3</td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;width:300px;height:0px;">10 <a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/beasts-of-chaos/Ungor-Raiders">Ungor Raiders</a></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;width:300px;height:0px;">10 <a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/beasts-of-chaos/Chaos-Warhounds">Chaos Warhounds</a></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;background-color:rgb(242,238,225);text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;width:40px;height:0px;">4</td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;background-color:rgb(242,238,225);text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;width:300px;height:0px;">10 <a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/beasts-of-chaos/Gors">Gors</a></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;background-color:rgb(242,238,225);text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;width:300px;height:0px;">2 <a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/beasts-of-chaos/Chaos-Spawn">Chaos Spawn</a></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;width:40px;height:0px;">5</td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;width:300px;height:0px;">10 <a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/beasts-of-chaos/Gors">Gors</a></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;width:300px;height:0px;"><a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/beasts-of-chaos/Cockatrice">Cockatrice</a></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;background-color:rgb(242,238,225);text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;width:40px;height:0px;">6</td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;background-color:rgb(242,238,225);text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;width:300px;height:0px;"><a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/beasts-of-chaos/Tuskgor-Chariots">Tuskgor Chariot</a></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;background-color:rgb(242,238,225);text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;width:300px;height:0px;"><a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/beasts-of-chaos/Jabberslythe">Jabberslythe</a></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div class="BreakInsideAvoid" "><table border="0" bordercolor="#888" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0" style="border-collapse:collapse;border-width:0px"><tbody><tr><td><table class=" customTable" border="1" bordercolor="#888" cellpadding="4" style="border-collapse:collapse;border-color:#908249;border-width:0px"><tbody><tr><td colspan="4" style="border-width:1px 1px 0 1px;background-color:rgb(144,130,73);color:rgb(255,255,255);vertical-align:bottom;width:0px;height:0px;"><b>ELITE RETINUE FOLLOWERS TABLE (uses 2 rolls, or 1 roll and 1 Glory Point)</b></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;background-color:rgb(209,200,166);text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;width:27,5px;height:0px;"><b>D6</b></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;background-color:rgb(209,200,166);text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;width:320px;height:0px;"><b>Brayherds</b></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;background-color:rgb(209,200,166);text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;width:320px;height:0px;"><b>Warherds</b></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;background-color:rgb(209,200,166);text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;width:320px;height:0px;"><b>Monstrous Beastherds</b></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;width:27,5px;height:0px;">1-2</td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;width:320px;height:0px;">20 <a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/beasts-of-chaos/Gors">Gors</a></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;width:320px;height:0px;">3 <a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/beasts-of-chaos/Bullgors">Bullgors</a></td><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;text-align:left;vertical-align:middle;width:320px;height:0px;">3 <a href="http://wahapedia.ru/aos/factions/beasts-of-chaos/Dragon-Ogors">Dragon Ogors</a></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width:1px 1px 1px 1px;background-color:rgb(242,238,225);text-align:center;vertical-align:middle;width:27,5px;height:0px;">3</td><td style="borde